Sentencas: ABO(3)-type oxides are recently being explored as solid electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The objective of this work was to study an ABO3-type perovskite oxide, YAlO3, for its electrical properties and its suitability as a solid electrolyte.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The undoped and doped compositions of Y1-xCaxAlO3-delta(x-0-0.25) have been synthesized.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The phase purity of the samples has been investigated by X-ray diffraction studies.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity studies have been performed using ac impedance spectroscopy in the range 200-800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The doped YAlO3 compositions exhibit a total conductivity of about 1 mS/cm at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The microstructural evaluation of the samples has been conducted by scanning electron microscopy and energy dispersive spectrum analysis.
Titulo: Solid-state synthesis and characterization of Ca-substituted YAlO3 as electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells
